title: Ranked 5v5 is Not Up
body: It is a roughly 8:00 on a Friday night and ranked 5's isn't up yet. Usually it is supposed to come on around 7 but it is not up today, is there a reason for this?

replies.body: I wasn't able to find any issues with the [ranked team schedule](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/209964886-Ranked-Teams-Schedule).  Hopefully, everything is okay now!

I wasn't online yesterday but I can give you the official schedules:
https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/209964886-Ranked-Teams-Schedule
Were you able to play since you posted?
